   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-a" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Are you kidding?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-d" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>...Are you serious?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-g" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you like gold more than your girl friend?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>Huh? My first love? Hahaha, my first love is money.<BR>When I first saw this 1gold, I felt shock as if I got hit by a lightening and was touched. Hence, I felt in love with money with all my heart. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-b" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>
I'm not joking, I'm serious.<BR>There are different kinds of people in this world and one of them is like me... the money-loving kind.<BR>
 </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-c" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>
...Why are you looking at me like that?<BR>Everyone thinks I'm obsessed with money, but who in the world doesn't like money! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>Out of all who claim to love money, I am the one who loves money the most. But hey, I've never cheated anyone!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Pero speaks aggressively) </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-e" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>Of course I'm being serious. Don't look at me that way. You can only make money on your own. There are sayings like...<BR>Singles make a gold but couples spend a gold. That is so true </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-f" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>I'm not being single because I am not good at relationships. It is because I can make more money while staying single...<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Pero is giving ridiculous excuses)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>If I make lots of money, a girlfriend will come along automatically. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-h" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero $<BR>I can state 20 reasons why gold is better than having a girlfriend right now. You can have 10 or 20 gold but they won't become jealous of each other. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-i" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Pero$<BR>Also gold don't eat gold. Girlfriends? They eat gold, of course they do.<BR>Otherwise, people in relationships will not need to buy lace handkerchiefs or designer bags for their girlfriends. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-accepting-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
